# Default desktop bindings

# Toggle panel visibility on Alt+MMB
Mouse 2 RI $[Mod1] EWMH-Toggle Mouse 2 RI $[Mod1]
#Mouse 2 RI $[Mod1] Panel-Toggle

# Toggle panel visibility with NumLock
Mouse 2 RI $[Mod1]2 EWMH-Toggle Mouse 2 RI $[Mod1]2
#Mouse 2 RI $[Mod1]2 Panel-Toggle

# Toggle panel between top bottom on Alt+Shift+MMB
Mouse 2 RI $[Mod2] Panel-Toggle-OnTop
Mouse 2 RI $[Mod2]2 Panel-Toggle-OnTop

# vim:ft=fvwm
